{"tid":588880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［日經］一人一個喺街見過最柒嘅事","createTime":"2018-03-11T13:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T14:00:38.000Z","uid":159699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9020e4f2e4e9d7fdcdb9af7091c99fb19453f91e","tid":588880,"uid":159699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"心情唔係咁好 想笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講一個先<br />\n<br />\n之前同啊媽等車<br />\n見到有人包咗㗎電車求婚<br />\n因為車上啲人好High好嘈<br />\n所以吸引咗我睇下佢地<br />\n第一眼睇落 一切都好似好正常<br />\n有氣球有裝飾咁<br />\n點知再睇真啲......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個氣球串咗MERRY ME"},{"pid":"664c25e66d00eb38ac2e007e38463fba469ede90","tid":588880,"uid":11285,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"無圖你話見到上帝裸跑都得啦"},{"pid":"549c553582627c4241ac888e6d96d448e0630b86","tid":588880,"uid":159699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無圖你話見到上帝裸跑都得啦</blockquote><br />\n真係無講大話㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到唔係好敢相信，仲問啊媽睇唔睇到<br />\n佢都話睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}